p: The morphology of larvae was obtained according to Oliveira and coworkers [ 25]. Briefly, the larvae were incubated with the nanoemulsion containing the major compound at 250 μg mL −1, since it induced the highest mortality. After, they were fixed on ethanol 70% and evaluated by scanning electron microscopy under low vacuum using a Tabletop Microscope TM3030Plus (Hitachi, Ibaraki, Japan).
